tune.name: Stockholm Branch Ruby Jubilee
tune.author: Mikael Georgii
tune.content:
\relative f' <<
  \new Voice {
    \clef treble
    \time 6/8
    \key f \major

    \repeat volta 2 {
      \partial 8 c8 |
      f8 f' d c a f |
      g8 a bes c, d e |
      f8 a d c a f |
      g8 a bes c d e |
      \break

      f8 f, f' d c a |
      g8 a bes c, d e |
      f8 a d c a f |
      c8 d e f4
    } \break

    \repeat volta 2 {
      e8 |
      d8 e f g f d |
      c8 d e f g a |
      g8 a bes c bes g |
      a8 bes b c d e |
      \break

      f8 e f g f d |
      c8 e f c a f |
      g8 bes d c a f |
      c8 d e f4
    }
  }

  \new ChordNames {
    \chordmode {
      s8 |
      f4. d:m | g:m c:7 | f d:m | g c:7 |
      f2. | g4.:m c:7 | f f/a | c s4

      s8 |
      bes4. c | f d:m | g:m c:7 | f f:7 |
      bes4. bes/d | f/a d:m | g:m f/a | c:7 f4
    }
  }
>>
